dataIdInfo.idAbs: This line data layer represents roads for Iowa County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Iowa_Roads_2017.gdb.[This data was produced to be suitable for use with Bullberry Systems, Inc. R³GIS Dispatch and Administrator 911 routing software, and other routing software based on an ESRI platform with Network Analyst extension.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
